{
  "text": "In the present study, we examined the toxic potentials of 10 fluoroquinolones on the Achilles tendon in this animal model. Furthermore, we also investigated the effects of nine compounds with different anti-inflammatory actions on pefloxacininduced Achilles tendon lesions, because the incidence of lesions induced by this drug was very high [CITATION_1] .",
